@poppingyolkcafe all the brunch items pls!!! 🤍
-banana caramel french toast
-ube pancakes
-breakfast burgers
-kimchi butter fried chicken benedict 

they have a variety of different brunch items like pancakes, crepes, waffles, omelettes, croissants sandwiches & more! portions are HUGE! 

perfect spot for a brunch meet up w/ friends + family!

I’ve tried the most popular matcha spots in LA… 

but @cafe_danzzan has to be one of my favorites 😍

🍵The Life is Matcha is basically a double matcha but I’m telling you this one is the perfect balance of strong yet sweet. My go-to!! ♥️ 

🍪 try their gochujang sea salt caramel cookie for something different!

why is @setnewport one of the best brunch spots in the OC?? 👀✨

lively ambience 
gorg outdoor patio
live DJ on Sundays (photobooth + rotating vendors) 
AMAZING BRUNCH FOOD 😍

Join Set Newport for their weekly DJ Sunday brunches or their monthly Bubbles and Beats! 

We loved everything we go on their brunch menu especially the crab cake eggs benedict with caviar 😍
Nothing better than ocean views and an amazing brunch. 

Definitely check them out! 

MAKE A RESY: https://www.sevenrooms.com/reservations/setsteakandsushipnb/gabriela-reyes

@sunrightteastudio has ALL the options for boba!
